	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Fighting game sprites themselves were often resized down from hand-drawn animation cels, using high-quality scaling algorithms, and then had outline effects (aka "<a href="http://pixel-zone.rpgdx.net/shtml/tut-selout1.shtml" class="postlink">selout</a>") applied.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Author:&nbsp;</td>
